"[{\"comment\": \"there NEEDS to be a way for us to not have that happen anymore   no  more ladder decks in casual   team 5 always talks about the hearthstone experience  well this is BY FAR the worst part of the hearthstone experience  FIX IT GODDAMNIT\", \"commentId\": \"37900\", \"commentDate\": \"1495588741\"}, {\"comment\": \"The new uninteractive cancer Silence Priest   Featuring Lyra  Battlecry open Solitaire exe   Because the designers made a dumbass card and had to overcompensate to look smart\", \"commentId\": \"37901\", \"commentDate\": \"1495589188\"}, {\"comment\": \"It was blizzard properly punishing you for being a disgusting pirate player\", \"commentId\": \"37902\", \"commentDate\": \"1495589627\"}, {\"comment\": \"Playing with Shaman  Warrior plays a taunt on Turn 2  3  4  5  6  7 and 8  Perfect curve  No need to think  Just play and press next turn  Dumbest deck  Even Face Hunter was better\", \"commentId\": \"37903\", \"commentDate\": \"1495589655\"}, {\"comment\": \"if you are rank 8000 legend this close to the end of the season why do you try your fucking heart out to win against rank 1 players who have never been legend before\", \"commentId\": \"37904\", \"commentDate\": \"1495590387\"}, {\"comment\": \"Im really sick of seeing Patches the Pirate  I want to know how many decks are running it  even as a defensive tool  So annoying Nearly all of my decks have a single Golakka Crawler\", \"commentId\": \"37905\", \"commentDate\": \"1495590540\"}, {\"comment\": \"casual really really fucking sucks as a mode right now\", \"commentId\": \"37906\", \"commentDate\": \"1495591151\"}, {\"comment\": \"Im in CHARGGGGGGGE NOW I made patches gold on day one release and never looked back   My solid gold pirate deck was beating heads in then and still does now  Embrace the poorly designed game known as Hearthstone and learn to exploit it instead of complaining  The game is a joke but not as big of a joke as the people who whine about it\", \"commentId\": \"3